Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.07,0:29:13.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}See the bunny bees and puffs of steam from singing kettles in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.76,0:29:24.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Red butterflies with forks and knives ,who like to make a meal of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.50,0:29:35.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Life is clockwork quick lightning slow faster on your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.44,0:29:47.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}So eat your sugared dream and face the day before it runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.07,0:29:13.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}從樹上嗡嗡叫的蜂巢看到小蜜蜂和一陣陣氣流
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.76,0:29:24.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}紅色的蝴蝶拿著刀叉好像在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.50,0:29:35.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}生活就像鬧鐘一樣在你舌尖流失
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.44,0:29:47.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}在他溜走之前 那就品嘗著你美味的夢面對著那一天
