Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1975,2520)\pos(642,686)}{\c&H59A819&)\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs36\bord2\shad0\c&HFDFFFF&\3c&H59A819&\fsp15\pos(650,569.429)}{\blur50\t(0,1390,0.5,\blur3)}{\c&HFDFFFF&\1a&HFF&\b0\3c&HA25C07&}等待繁星之人\N{\fs25\fsp0}【中篇】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到森林圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我是森林的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不對  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說  我只是想讓你安心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙是進不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能解釋自己為什麼能看得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  做了壞事的傢伙是進不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不如說是不允許進來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都熱衷於讀書  不會傷害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,找個地方坐下  慢慢地享受時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有合適的書籍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡好久都沒人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這裡能有你喜歡的書就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,應該說找一本會喜歡你的書才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,擅自跑進來  非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事情完全不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,稍…稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  應該是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就這個好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫理一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦理一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥…智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,借書證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為了能回到這裡  記得要帶好借書證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了  出去之後要徑直跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸我可累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我說  和別人說話的時候能別玩手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了稍微等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都這樣  完全把我的話當耳邊風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我每天都是怎麼過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  我也是很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都是她的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,現在全是我在照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,當初是你沒多加考慮就說收養她  所以她才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你當時不也同意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那還不是因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,別碰  聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大輝  你也趕快去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要來我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都因為你  媽媽才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小姑娘  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\c&H334055&\frz122.1\pos(376,495)}暑假作業②讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我能來看書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,借書證有帶著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有這張借書證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是本館的使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,隨時都能前來  也可以借閱書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每次僅限一本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還有就是進出時要隨手關門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要遵守了這些規則  每天都能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  每天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可以盡情地閱覽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到森林圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我家真的已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  老婆帶著孩子都搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我家已經照顧夠久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這回該輪到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你也完全喜歡上書了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  看書的時候可以忘記一切煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  羽鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的話  一直待在這裡也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒想好寫哪本書的讀後感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,明明讀了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因為都很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼書?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那本是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都放在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那本是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想  是一本什麼樣的書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那選哪一本好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,閱讀書的最後一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讀後感還…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不早點回去的話  媽媽不會擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人會擔心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為阿姨都搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  這都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老在意那些怪東西  經常惹阿姨生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就今天這次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,僅限今天  下不為例
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓你寫出讀後感的書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那一天我就是不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是少見  智世居然會如此固執
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為當時我還是個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,路茲  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你不痛苦就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然後  然後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.07,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然後  那一夜就成了特殊的一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我有本書想送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「孤零零的小星星」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,連環畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你一定需要這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  能幫我收拾一下這裡的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,「孤零零的小星星」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在漆冷的虛無夜空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有一顆小星星在那裡獨自發著光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,日出前 一定要把她送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:24:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再見  你再也無法進來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.83,0:25:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.91,0:25:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.93,0:25:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.01,0:25:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.40,0:25:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.87,0:25:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你還能進來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.39,0:25:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.65,0:26:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.79,0:26:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你關門了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.10,0:26:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.07,0:26:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.49,0:26:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.20,0:26:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.25,0:27:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快點  快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.47,0:27:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.70,0:27:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.83,0:27:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.56,0:27:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.80,0:27:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這本書借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.78,0:27:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,記得一定要還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.15,0:27:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.22,0:27:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.96,0:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.22,0:27:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.23,0:28:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  它們都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.95,0:28:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.83,0:28:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我沒忘記關門的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.03,0:28:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥智世  我有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.35,0:28:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能把這本書送到某人手中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.52,0:28:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我已經做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.89,0:28:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.31,0:28:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.03,0:28:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.84,0:29:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,未能遵守的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.07,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,身負青年的遺恨
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.08,0:30:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,少女奔跑了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,向著未知的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.62,0:30:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓…
Comment: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:10.43,Comment,,0,0,0,,
